<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA90">
<l>cilampuñ ceṟikaḻaluñ ceṉṟicaippa viṇṇā</l>
<l>ṟalampiya cēvaṭipō yaṇṭam – pulampiyatō</l>
<l>ḷeṇṭicaiyuñ cūḻa viṭampōtā teṉkolō</l>
<l>vaṇṭuḻāy mālaḷanta maṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [his] red feet that were rinsed in the heavenly river go [to the top of the world] egg,</l>
<l>so that [his] foot rings and tight anklets sound in movement,</l>
<l>[and his] sole arms encompass all the eight directions, which place did it not reach,</l>
<l>the earth that was measured by Māl with lush tulsi?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
